you're thinking it's too late
and you're gonna be a fatalist

62
00:05:11,010 --> 00:05:12,409
and let it all go to hell.

63
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:14,876
But, George, if you keep performing
the way you are,

64
00:05:14,981 --> 00:05:18,917
