93
00:07:34,253 --> 00:07:37,950
Honey, if you don't get into
a decent college...

94
00:07:38,057 --> 00:07:41,515
- I'm gonna go watch TV.
- No, you will not watch TV.

95
00:07:41,627 --> 00:07:42,855
You will stay here

96
00:07:42,962 --> 00:07:46,159
