(SHOUTING) Find something!

115
00:09:00,907 --> 00:09:02,875
- Hey.
- Hey.

116
00:09:06,078 --> 00:09:08,740
- I'm Sally.
- I know.

117
00:09:08,848 --> 00:09:10,315
Thanks for covering for me.

118
00:09:10,416 --> 00:09:12,509
No problem.

119
00:09:13,152 --> 00:09:14,779
Why did you?

120
00:09:15,988 --> 00:09:17,512
I don't know.

121
00:09:17,690 --> 00:09:19,157
You were doing something so renegade,

122
00:09:19,258 --> 00:09:20,691
I thought you deserved to get away with it.

123
00:09:21,894 --> 00:09:23,623
I run afoul of the authorities so often,

124
00:09:23,729 --> 00:09:26,289
I figured I could handle it better than you.

125
00:09:27,767 --> 00:09:29,496
You're really weird.

126
00:09:33,639 --> 00:09:35,607
SALLY: So, why don't you ever
do your work?

127
00:09:35,741 --> 00:09:37,766
There are so many more important things
to think about,

128
00:09:37,877 --> 00:09:40,311
