00:11:12,705 --> 00:11:14,832
I'm drinking wine out of a tumbler.

155
00:11:15,374 --> 00:11:16,363
What do you want, George?

156
00:11:18,778 --> 00:11:20,803
CHARLOTTE: And this was before
we left the sticks.

157
00:11:20,946 --> 00:11:22,971
So, I cock one eye, look down,

158
00:11:23,749 --> 00:11:26,877
expecting to see a giant water bug,

159
00:11:26,986 --> 00:11:28,681
or a water moccasin, or...

160
00:11:30,222 --> 00:11:33,316
Water something. Something I had to kill.

161
00:11:33,426 --> 00:11:35,621
But it was the pilot's hand!

162
00:11:35,728 --> 00:11:36,695
Oh!

163
00:11:38,631 --> 00:11:39,996
Ticklish, this one!

164
00:11:40,132 --> 00:11:41,099
(CHARLOTTE GIGGLING)

165
00:11:41,801 --> 00:11:43,234
Let me get you a paper towel.

166
00:11:43,669 --> 00:11:47,537
You know,
ticklish people make great lovers.

167
00:11:48,474 --> 00:11:50,601
Everything is erogenous.

168
00:11:53,079 --> 00:11:55,206
My God. She's amazing.

169
00:11:55,815 --> 00:11:57,407
Not if you're her daughter.

170
00:11:58,050 --> 00:11:59,608
How'd you end up in New York?

171
00:11:59,719 --> 00:12:04,019
My mom had me when she was 16.
My dad was a truck driver,

172
00:12:04,123 --> 00:12:06,387
and one day he took off
and never came back.

173
00:12:06,492 --> 00:12:07,959
And this was?

174
00:12:08,060 --> 00:12:10,654
Clarksburg. It's a small town in Tennessee.

175
00:12:11,697 --> 00:12:14,996
This rich guy from New York,
who owned a textile plant,

176
00:12:15,101 --> 00:12:20,733
started coming down, and it was like
we were castaways and he was the ship.

177
00:12:21,907 --> 00:12:23,499
But I ended up here,

178
00:12:23,609 --> 00:12:29,047
eight years old, new school,
new friends, fancy new clothes.

179
00:12:29,882 --> 00:12:31,440
My mom divorced him a year ago,

180
00:12:31,550 --> 00:12:34,610
and now she's back on the singles scene
with a vengeance.

181
00:12:38,624 --> 00:12:41,684
I do think I should
get some homework done, though.

182
00:12:43,496 --> 00:12:46,522
I should get going then.
Got work to do myself.

183
00:12:47,066 --> 00:12:48,499
Yeah, right.

184
00:12:56,275 --> 00:12:57,401
Thank you.

185
00:12:58,544 --> 00:12:59,704
Goodbye.

