VIVIAN: I know.

189
00:13:33,746 --> 00:13:36,214
But you never think it's gonna be
the people that it's gonna be.

190
00:13:36,315 --> 00:13:39,682
- JACK: They've been together for 15 years.
- I know. It's certainly ridiculous.

191
00:13:39,785 --> 00:13:42,151
- What happened to the electricity?
- Hi, sweetie.

192
00:13:42,254 --> 00:13:44,882
We got take-out
from the rotisserie chicken place.

193
00:13:44,990 --> 00:13:46,252
Grab a plate and join us.

194
00:13:46,358 --> 00:13:48,349
But the lights. What happened?

195
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:51,827
It's my fault. I forgot to pay the bill.

196
00:13:51,931 --> 00:13:53,831
And it's no big deal.
They'll be on tomorrow.

197
00:13:56,468 --> 00:13:57,662
George, we're trying to turn

198
00:13:57,770 --> 00:13:59,670
this awkward little mix-up
into a fun experience.

199
00:13:59,772 --> 00:14:02,468
And if you can't get into
the spirit of adventure,

200
00:14:02,575 --> 00:14:05,942
then you can just do your own thing.
You don't have to stick around.

201
00:14:06,045 --> 00:14:07,842
I'm sorry, Jack. I can't use my laptop,

202
00:14:07,947 --> 00:14:09,847
much less get my assignments.

203
00:14:09,949 --> 00:14:13,544
So, go to the library or Starbucks.
Be resourceful.

204
