but with an insect,

224
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:33,021
the tiniest, humblest creature in nature.

225
00:15:35,034 --> 00:15:36,695
Which is pretty Romantic.

226
00:15:39,738 --> 00:15:41,797
I think you just found
your term paper, George.

227
00:15:53,319 --> 00:15:54,445
George!

228
00:15:54,553 --> 00:15:55,520
Hi.

229
00:15:58,390 --> 00:16:00,654
- Come join us.
- Cool.

